Project: To-Do List Application

Summary:
A To-Do List Application allows users to keep track of their tasks and schedule. The application will have the following features:

Add a task
Mark a task as complete
Edit a task
Delete a task
Display a list of all tasks, including their status (complete/incomplete)
The application will be built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The tasks will be stored in the browser's local storage, allowing the user to access their tasks even after they close the application. The user interface will be intuitive and easy to use, making it an effective tool for task management.
